title: Why Bert Told His Fiancé He Wouldn't Fight For Her
description:
Would you fight for someone if they were interested in someone else? It's the question Bert's fiancée, Tiffany, asked him...and he answered within SECONDS. And he told her no, he wouldn't fight for her. And here's why.
